{"tid":122011,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女友出來社會工作後的的第一個情人節就分左手","createTime":"2017-02-15T16:32:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T07:34:44.000Z","uid":48631,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"02710afff065acf090727fd846dec36fcb44449d","tid":122011,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:32:00.000Z","msg":"我同女友係中學同學,中學畢業之後佢入左city,我就讀HKDI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢讀緊書個陣都好地地,但自從佢上年畢左業出黎做野之後就成個人變成晒<br />\n以前佢唔好名牌,而家成身都係名牌,出街食野間餐廳一定要裝修得夠靚,就算食上海婆婆都嫌cheap,仲成日嫌我搵得錢少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我今個情人節都醒醒定定架啦,晨早book左食outback,但我一見到佢就即刻西我面,話點解人地同事個男朋友可以送99枝玫瑰但我一枝都冇(過左咁多個情人節我除左第一年送過一枝之外不嬲都冇送,佢以前仲曾經話情人節買玫瑰花咁貴不如食左佢好過),成程食飯都西我面<br />\n好啦食完到咁上下我拎左份禮物出黎,係我自己上workshop整既皮散紙包卡片袋,因為我知佢手袋呀銀包都係新買既名牌,所以送手造卡片袋畀佢,諗住冇錢就誠意搭救,點知佢一見到好嬲話我敷衍佢,問我係咪仲當佢係中學生,數下數下又嫌我人工低唔長進,我忍唔住話佢變到好貪慕虛榮,佢一忍到之後話我侮辱佢即刻走左<br />\n我今日send極whatsapp+打電話畀佢都唔聽,啱啱先whatsapp我話分手,facebook仲要神速變做單身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77bcc344d2d249eab3aa62c2838b6a1b0d117537","tid":122011,"uid":37129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:32:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12fcde229dc2cd0aff58b5598c706fa48d71c84f","tid":122011,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:32:53.000Z","msg":"我真係好想知佢識左d乜野朋友搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6836b4dd39395f8b371433e621313440cde218e1","tid":122011,"uid":82030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:34:01.000Z","msg":"做邊行呀佢？"},{"pid":"952e3d6d1036d558e2b02ab017297e882c431823","tid":122011,"uid":46832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:34:38.000Z","msg":"反正價值觀都變左，分開都係一件好事"},{"pid":"f7c23453bde7fef0b5933a5f6285b4627158ba39","tid":122011,"uid":16085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:36:37.000Z","msg":"學巴打話齋<br />\n<br />\n入大學 同 大學畢業 係對感情既兩大難關"},{"pid":"4cde793b71d450923c041073763753c8adcd1c43","tid":122011,"uid":19265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:38:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">跟住你好快見到佢有一個有錢嘅「新」男朋友</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a459a9850a95cd779a813d562cf40ff4c35f75","tid":122011,"uid":19028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:38:23.000Z","msg":"早散早著 呢d女遲早比帽你 <br />\nBtw 雞始終都係.."},{"pid":"b5dd44a66db24594cc614b1fb08956265faeec19","tid":122011,"uid":36679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:38:44.000Z","msg":"可能識左d有錢佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59527c74a20871ae89b4457cb9bb90e66040d781","tid":122011,"uid":27049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:38:54.000Z","msg":"come on james <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"627ffc0ef6627523ab737fb1f8c4e18c9461d232","tid":122011,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:39:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做邊行呀佢？</blockquote><br />\n入左間代理外國大brand既公司做legal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02f6ae550a92c21d2f0465a7de3bd2cd7237ec99","tid":122011,"uid":20299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:40:45.000Z","msg":"Fresh grad就要求咁高要99支<br />\n到時求婚點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b9007943f6ad8f79e7a913b2b87ef6c3cd78bc2","tid":122011,"uid":84292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:41:14.000Z","msg":"呢啲港女分手好過啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c7b